{{xsee|[[hood]]|[['hood|’hood]]}}

==English==

===Etymology===
From {{OE.}} [[-hád]] or [[-hǽd]], via {{ME.}} [[-hode]] or [[-hed]]

===Pronunciation===
* [[Wiktionary:Pronunciation_key|IPA]]: /hʊd/

===Noun suffix===
'''-hood''' (''uncountable'')
# a [[condition]] or [[state]] of the word it is suffixed to.
#: ''child - childhood''
#: ''neighbor - neighborhood''
# a [[group]] sharing a specified condition or state
#: ''brother - brotherhood''

